{
  "stem": "23096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the shock maybe burnt it in, where some of the details outside and stuff-- what happened before, what happened after-- are so immaterial that I just-- you just don't pay no attention to it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we lived day by day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were lucky to see another morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so a lot of the details I-- I don't-- I don't really remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the details, the pictures inside-- I could sit down and draw you pictures.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- they're that-- almost that clear in my mind yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm mm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't personally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, there weren't very many walking around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was only just a very, very few-- if there was a half a dozen walking around, that was a lot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were in no condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I'm sure some of them-- when more people probably got in there that could-- could speak German or something, it may have-- may have made a difference the-- to find out-- I don't-- we don't know what nationalities they were, whether they were Jewish, or political, or-- or what.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don-- we-- there-- we don't know too much about Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the only camp that they don't have the statistics-- how many people were-- had gone through the camp, who the people were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the other camps, they have all the records.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They can tell you who went through the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they took excellent records.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- but I don't know why, that being the first camp, they took everything, and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] on the-- more or less the barracks type of buildings, there must have been [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a couple dozen, at least.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was pretty good sized camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
